    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "We just met yesterday with the folks at [Hypothes.is](http://hypothes.is/) to discuss how we could use their system to annotate/comment on notebooks.  I think I am preferring that type of a approach as it is more flexible and doesn't require creating a new cell type that interferes with the main content.  Could you have a look at their stuff and add that to the IPEP?\n"
