    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "Thanks for the comments. I will follow all your suggestions and try to understand what work is involved. However I would first like to clarify that what I'm suggesting is no more that an identifiable cell type with configurable styling. I now think \"Remark\" may be more descriptive of what I have in mind, not full blown multi-user commenting or sophisticated annotation. A \"remark\" would serve no purpose other that of say a teachers scribbling in the margins to highlight something that needs more work/thought and that would be omitted from the final document. Please do let me know though if I'm still over-simplifying the effort involved. Thanks again. \n"
